Package it.polimi.GC13.view.GUI

Interface Getter

All Known Implementing Classes:
GoldCardGetter, ObjectiveCardGetter, ResourceCardGetter, ResourceGetter, StarterCardGetter
public interface Getter
The Getter interface defines a method for retrieving the URL of a resource based on its name. Implementations of this interface can be used to load various types of resources in the game GUI.

    Method

    URL
    getURL(String resourceName)
